data.description: Motivated Seller!  OUTBUILDING MEGA SPACE   Picture this: a modest but mighty home on nearly an acre of land, complete with TWO giant barns (1st barn is two levels of 1440 sq.ft. for a total of 2880 sq.ft. & 2nd barn 1653 sq.ft. + upstairs storage with electricity on a separate meter and a wood burning stove in the office. ) for all your projects and hobbies (and the hobbies of all your friends). The property is located close to all the conveniences of New Albany, but with a peaceful, rural feel. The home has been recently updated with new flooring, cabinets, appliances, and lighting in the kitchen, as well as a remodeled bathroom. And let's not forget about the property's unique car "lift" - a true gem for car enthusiasts! Imagine the possibilities with this much space for your projects and outdoor activities. It's the perfect blend of country living and modern convenience. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
